on&amp;author=C+Oprian&amp;author=T+Kim&amp;author=S+Rahimtoola&amp;publication_year=1993&amp;journal=N+Engl+J+Med&amp;pages=1289-1296&amp;doi=10.1056%2FNEJM199305063281801&amp;pmid=8469251">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">7.</div><div id="r7" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Horstkotte D, Loogen F. The natural history of aortic valve stenosis. <em>Eur Heart J</em> 1988;9(suppl E):57–64.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1093/eurheartj/9.suppl_E.57">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/3042404/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=The+natural+history+of+aortic+valve+stenosis&amp;author=D+Horstkotte&amp;author=F+Loogen&amp;publication_year=1988&amp;journal=Eur+Heart+J&amp;pages=57-64&amp;doi=10.1093%2Feurheartj%2F9.suppl_E.57&amp;pmid=3042404">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">8.</div><div id="r8" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Bose AK, Aitchison JD, Dark JH. Aortic valve replacement in octogenarians. <em>J Cardiothorac Surg</em> 2007;2:33.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1186/1749-8090-2-33">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17629905/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Aortic+valve+replacement+in+octogenarians&amp;author=AK+Bose&amp;author=JD+Aitchison&amp;author=JH+Dark&amp;publication_year=2007&amp;journal=J+Cardiothorac+Surg&amp;pages=33&amp;doi=10.1186%2F1749-8090-2-33&amp;pmid=17629905">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="lab